doc.name: XBrowser_Unfocus
doc.summary: Has no affect, included for backwards compatibility

description.p: The XBrowser_Unfocus command has no affect and is included for backwards compatibility with older applications.
The instanceId is the integer identifier of a browser object
The XBrowser_Unfocus command puts empty into the result
Note: For general information on using the browser library, see the notes in the revBrowserOpen function reference.
